Package avdta.demand

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AST
    This represents an assignment interval, which is used when generating demand.
    DemandImportFromVISTA
    This class defines methods to convert demand data from the VISTA data format to the AVDTA data format.
    DemandProfile
    A demand profile is a set of assignment intervals.
    DemandProfileRecord
    This class represents an entry in DemandProject.getDemandProfileFile().
    DemandRecord
    This class represents an entry in the DemandProject.getDemandFile().
    DynamicODRecord
    This class represents an entry in the DemandProject.getDynamicODFile() file.
    DynamicODTable
    This class provides an interface for modifying and printing the dynamic OD and static OD tables.
    ReadDemandNetwork
    This includes methods to create and read demand
    StaticODRecord
    This class represents an entry in the DemandProject.getStaticODFile() file.
